 />"},{"pid":"2fd21fc50accfbec4fa87c9f980f9d28ab0b3f02","tid":836941,"uid":45376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔會拉到架<br />\n因為根本唔係得一兩個放可以鎖定人黎拉而係好多柒頭都會買黎放<br />\n每逢過時過節嘅夜晚只要你顎高頭望你總會望到2~3個燈飛緊<br />\n而差佬咁淆底亦都盡可能避開唔會入村做野"},{"pid":"a3e98c8c4e88a256c4cbb3639ffe9e626a3fc079","tid":836941,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"淋病之前收唔到大西北棕地，淆晒，仲話好打得"},{"pid":"e18099df3602e70e19f6c852a8f73d08aaf7eff1","tid":836941,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3e98c8c4e88a256c4cbb3639ffe9e626a3fc079","tid":836941,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"淋病之前收唔到大西北棕地，淆晒，仲話好打得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"村屋僭建都無聲無色咁收曬皮"},{"pid":"4d728afce085ac5f9846e5c147f81147b5ea5028","tid":836941,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e18099df3602e70e19f6c852a8f73d08aaf7eff1","tid":836941,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3e98c8c4e88a256c4cbb3639ffe9e626a3fc079","tid":836941,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T06:44:48.000Z","msg":"淋病之前收唔到大西北棕地，淆晒，仲話好打得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"村屋僭建都無聲無色咁收曬皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"呢個真係經典<br />\n開頭聲大大, 點知無貨賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n齋嗌口號, 無實際行動<br />\n而家仲要同鄉黑拎選票<br />\n攪到姓劉既得閒隔一排就出黎屌下佢兩句<br />\n一d 威嚴都無撚晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}